rows.label: qst200713_msg0001
rows.name:
I-I'm saved-mau. I'm
glad to be alive-mau...

rows.label: qst200713_msg0002
rows.name:
Honestly... If we hadn't been
here, you'd be their food by now.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm grateful for
that-mau. Thank you-mau.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0004
rows.name:
But, howeeeeever! A
match is a match-mau!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0005
rows.name:
Just because you saved me, Maumau
won't go easy on you-mau!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0006
rows.name: You're still going? You never learn...

rows.label: qst200713_msg0020
rows.name:
...That said, this area is full
of Ignas and is dangerous-mau.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0008
rows.name:
It would be safer for you
all if we call a temporary
truce and cooperate-mau.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0009
rows.name:
Isn't that just because
you're scared, Maumau?

rows.label: qst200713_msg0012
rows.name:
I'm not the one in the contest, so
Idaten should decide what to do.

rows.label: qst200713_msg0014
rows.name: He's not listening at all, mo...

rows.label: qst200713_msg0017
rows.name:
The smell of mushrooms is
closer than before-ppo! The
Mashimashidake is nearby-ppo!

rows.label: qst200713_msg0018
rows.name:
He says. If you're scared of
being alone, don't fall behind.
